name: SA.I.dekick
text: Target face-up cards your opponent controls equal to the number of Cyberse monsters you control with 2300 original ATK; negate their effects until the end of this turn. You can banish this card from your GY, then target 1 of your banished Cyberse monsters; Special Summon it. You can only use each effect of "SA.I.dekick" once per turn.
